Events.RelatedDescription: Merged pull request "Move namespace resolver into framework" (#1370) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK
Events.RelatedBody: This allows all implementations to automatically get the default namespace resolver. This doesn't add extra types and is just the default data.

Merged pull request "Use OrdinalIgnoreCase in LINQ generator" (#1367) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK
Events.RelatedBody: Without this, the current culture is used. Since .NET Framework and .NET Core use different data sources for culture sorting, this caused differences from the CLI and VS. This should keep the generated source consistent across toolchains.
